title: Will the top song on Spotify Charts hit 30.5M global streams for the week ending on March 24?
description:

It means not every stream on Spotify is eligible for Charts. Some songs may have fewer chart-eligible streams than others, depending on streaming behavior.

If Spotify remains down or unavailable this market will resolve to 50-50. If Spotify goes out of business before resolution time, this question will resolve to “No”.
